						 <p>This feels way too dangerous for the Foundation to test so extensively. It caused a Site to catch fire in order to fulfil its command, so the risk of malevolent genie action seems too high – especially when you consider that there's no apparent limit to this object's powers.</p> <p>I'd also echo the gist of Abettik's comment, although perhaps not its coarseness.</p> 
				 	]]>
